title: Scene2_1c
---
It seems that this is the only way, you alone must explore that old and mysterious house.

“It’s fine, Delphine. Nothing different from what happened last time, and Mom and Dad won’t know. You just need to open the door and take a look at the mirror.”

You cheer yourself up in a low voice, hugging the doll Del.

