title: Vision2_1
---
<<set $visionSubject to "friends">>

You see the reflection of yourself and your friends - Jules, Ash, and River. 

You are standing on the side of the street, but {$moves} is not standing with you.

They are standing next to a car, which adults are filling with large boxes.

Where is {$moves} going? Are they moving away? Why?

Your thoughts are a mess.

You always thought you, Jules, Ash, and River would be close friends forever.

You never wished to separate from any of them. You don’t even know how to contact {$moves} after separation.

You don't know whether you will meet again.

<<jump Vision2_4>>
