title: Vision2_2
---
<<set $visionSubject to "family">>

You see the reflection of yourself and your mom.

You're doing homework, and your mom is preparing dinner for both of you with a tired face.

Where's Dad?

In your memory, whenever Mom is tired, Dad will always help her, especially when she's just got home from work.

But you can’t find your dad anywhere in the reflection. Is he still at work? Or has he gone away?

Thinking becomes messy, and bad thoughts pop up one after another.

You dare not continue to contemplate.

<<jump Vision2_4>>
===

title: Vision2_3
---
<<set $visionSubject to "yourself">>

You see the reflection of yourself.

You're at a new school...could it be the high school?

Other students gather with their friends to have lunch together. But you walk out of the classroom alone, take your lunch and find a quiet place to eat where no one is around.

“Where are my friends? Jules, Ash, and River?” you ask the mirror, but the mirror will not answer you.

Will your friends get tired of you? Will they be in different classes? Will you be all alone this year and the next?

There’s only silence in the room. All you can do is think.

<<jump Vision2_4>>
===

