You should be leaving, although what you have just seen makes it difficult for you to do so calmly.

You have to meet up with your friends, and can’t let them see what you are thinking.

And you need to get some candy. Your parents will be worried if you come home empty-handed.

You leave the house and close the door carefully behind you.

